<section id="craft" class="relative py-24 md:py-32 bg-ink text-cream grain">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
    <div class="md:col-span-5 relative">
      <div class="aspect-[4/5] relative overflow-hidden rounded-sm">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559525839-d9acfd032c68?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80" alt="Slow roasted coffee beans cooling in a copper drum — Meridian artisan coffee roaster" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 ring-1 ring-copper/30 ring-inset"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 md:-left-8 bg-copper text-cream p-4 md:p-5 rounded-sm shadow-xl max-w-[200px]">
        <div class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] opacity-80">Field Note 03</div>
        <div class="font-display italic text-base leading-snug mt-1">"Every good cup begins in the hands of someone you'll never meet."</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-6 md:col-start-7">
      <div class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-copper mb-4">§ The Craft</div>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight mb-8">A Roast that Respects<br/>the Hands that Grew It.</h2>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-[15px] md:text-base leading-relaxed opacity-85">
        <p>Meridian was founded on a quiet conviction: that specialty coffee is not a premium label, but a chain of small devotions from seed to sip. We buy from farms we have walked. We pay well above commodity. We roast in small batches, by ear and by eye, until the bean tells us to stop.</p>
        <p>Our roaster sits at the meridian of two worlds — the tropics, where the cherry ripens, and the city, where it is finally brewed. Between those two points lives everything we care about: patience, traceability, and the refusal to hide behind a blend.</p>
        <p><a href="/our-story" class="text-copper border-b border-copper/40 hover:border-copper transition pb-0.5">Read the full founding story →</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-cream/15">
        <div><div class="font-display text-3xl text-copper">03</div><div class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] opacity-60 mt-1">Origin Farms</div></div>
        <div><div class="font-display text-3xl text-copper">48h</div><div class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] opacity-60 mt-1">Roast to Ship</div></div>
        <div><div class="font-display text-3xl text-copper">200%</div><div class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] opacity-60 mt-1">Above Fair Trade</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
